activity.value: Wylam Brewery operates as a craft brewery, producing and distributing real ale in cask and keg formats. Located in the historic Palace of Arts building in Exhibition Park, the brewery has revitalized a landmark structure from the 1929 North East Exhibition.  Beyond brewing, Wylam Brewery offers a multifaceted experience, including a public Brewery Tap open Thursdays to Sundays, a Grand Hall hosting live music, weddings, corporate events, and pop-up experiences.  As a pioneer in the craft beer movement, Wylam Brewery has been brewing "proper beer" since 2000, predating the widespread adoption of the "craft beer" term.  Their commitment to quality and heritage is evident in their use of traditional brewing methods and their dedication to creating a vibrant community hub within their brewery space.
